text: Tomi Jaakko Poikolainen is a retired archer from Finland. He was born on 27 December 1961. Poikolainen competed at the 1980, 1984, 1988, 1992, and the 1996 Summer Olympics.Tomi PoikolainenTomi POIKOLAINEN == References == Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for Finland Category:Olympic silver medalists for Finland
